---
// Sense props per ara — les dades són estàtiques
// Quan tinguem Sanity les podrem extreure d'aquí
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- ── ESQUERRA ── -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center
              px-8 lg:px-16 pt-32 pb-16 lg:py-0"
  >
    <!-- Tag -->
    <h1
      class="hero-item inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-coral text-xs
             uppercase tracking-[0.18em] font-medium mb-8 opacity-0"
    >
      <span class="block w-8 h-px bg-coral"></span>
      SEO per a dones emprenedores
    </h1>

    <!-- H1 -->
    <p
      class="hero-item font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-black
             leading-none text-offwhite opacity-0"
    >
      Posiciona el<br />
      teu negoci<br />
      sense perdre<br />
      <em class="italic text-coral">el teu estil</em>
    </p>

    <!-- Subtítol -->
    <p
      class="hero-item mt-6 text-sand font-light text-lg leading-relaxed
             max-w-md opacity-0"
    >
      T'ajudem a apareixer a Google quan les teves clientes et busquen. SEO
      estratègic pensat per a negocis femenins que volen créixer de veritat.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="hero-item flex flex-wrap items-center gap-5 mt-10 opacity-0">
      <a href="/contacte" class="btn-primary"> Vull una auditoria </a>
      <a href="/serveis" class="btn-secondary"> Veure serveis → </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="hero-item flex gap-10 mt-14 opacity-0">
      {
        [
          { num: "+120", label: "Negocis posicionats" },
          { num: "3×", label: "Tràfic de mitjana" },
          { num: "8 anys", label: "D'experiència" },
        ].map(({ num, label }) => (
          <div>
            <div class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-offwhite leading-none">
              {num}
            </div>
            <div class="text-sand text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-1.5">
              {label}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── DRETA ── -->
  <div class="relative hidden lg:block">
    <!-- Fons forma diagonal -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-dark-sand"
      style="clip-path: polygon(8% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%)"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Targeta de resultats -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center px-12">
      <div
        class="hero-card w-full max-w-sm bg-white/4 border border-white/10
               backdrop-blur-sm p-8 opacity-0"
      >
        <p class="text-coral text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-6">
          📈 Resultats d'una clienta — 6 mesos
        </p>

        {
          [
            { label: "Visibilitat", value: "+312%", width: "88%" },
            { label: "Posicions Top 3", value: "+24 kw", width: "72%" },
            { label: "Tràfic orgànic", value: "+3.1k/m", width: "95%" },
            { label: "Vendes online", value: "+78%", width: "65%" },
          ].map(({ label, value, width }) => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-3.5 border-b border-white/8 last:border-0">
              <span class="text-sand text-sm w-32 shrink-0">{label}</span>
              <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/8 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div
                  class="metric-bar absolute left-0 top-0 h-full bg-coral"
                  style={`width: ${width}`}
                />
              </div>
              <span class="text-offwhite text-sm font-medium w-16 text-right shrink-0">
                {value}
              </span>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decoració — cercle coral difuminat -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2
             w-96 h-96 bg-coral/15 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 lg:left-16 flex items-center gap-3
              text-sand/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest"
  >
    <div class="scroll-line w-px h-10 bg-sand/20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full bg-coral animate-scroll-line">
      </div>
    </div>
    Scroll
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Animació entrada elements hero */
  .hero-item {
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-item:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  .hero-item:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
  .hero-item:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }
  .hero-item:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 0.7s;
  }
  .hero-item:nth-child(5) {
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Barres de mètriques */
  .metric-bar {
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    animation: growBar 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes growBar {
    to {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }
  }

  /* Scroll indicator */
  @keyframes scrollLine {
    0% {
      height: 0;
      top: 0;
    }
    50% {
      height: 100%;
      top: 0;
    }
    100% {
      height: 0;
      top: 100%;
    }
  }

  .animate-scroll-line {
    animation: scrollLine 2s ease infinite;
  }

  /* Delay barres en cascada */
  .metric-bar:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
  }
  .metric-bar:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 1.4s;
  }
  .metric-bar:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 1.6s;
  }
  .metric-bar:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 1.8s;
  }

  /* Targeta hero */
  .hero-card {
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.2s ease forwards;
  }
</style>
